        "subject": "LU-2456 lnet: Dynamic LNet Configuration (DLC) config routing",
        "message": "LU-2456 lnet: Dynamic LNet Configuration (DLC) config routing\n\nThis is the second patch of a set of patches that enables DLC.\n\nThis patch adds the following features to LNET.  Currently these\nfeatures are not driven by user space.\n- Adding/Deleting routs\n- Enabling/disabling routing\n- Configure routing buffer pools\n\nSigned-off-by: Amir Shehata <amir.shehata@intel.com>\nChange-Id: I6ed68ad116016cd1b63f9ca7ac6450fdb0ddc899\n"
      },
